\f1\b0\fs26 \cf4 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 Surf House Baja is a 4-bedroom beach house designed for an elevated surf experience. The open-plan kitchen and resident, local fishermen give you a real opportunity to cooking up a feast, while friends hang out at the counter surrounded by playful swing seating suspended from the ceiling. \
