\f0\b \cb3 \
Property details	
\f1\b0\fs26 \cf4 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 Surf House Baja has 4 uniquely designed bedrooms all with access to the ocean front balcony. Wake up to a view of the ocean and a point break wave you will be eager to jump in and surf. \
\
The open-plan kitchen has plenty of space for cooking up a feast, while friends can hang out at the counter on playful swings suspended from the ceiling.\
\
The dining area seats six, and there\'92s an even bigger table on the patio for lively group meals under the stars.\
\
Upstairs, the first two bedrooms have floor to ceiling ocean facing windows, each with double beds, crisp white linens, and storage space. The third bedroom has a queen bed and a writing desk, while the fourth has a cozy single. Need extra sleeping space? The large upstairs hallway has a guest sofa bed. \
\
Step out onto the balcony for morning stretches, sun-soaked afternoons, or sunset cocktails.\
The bathroom keeps it simple with a spacious hot shower, hand-built furnishings, and plenty of fresh towels. \
\
Outside, unwind in the sand garden with hammocks, swings, and a fire pit, perfect for starlit conversations. \
\
Feeling competitive? The garage has a ping pong table ready for action. Plus, there\'92s a surfboard rack with foam boards and a stash of used wetsuits, so you can get everyone in the ocean. \

