\cf6 \cb7 Nearby Activities	
\f1\b0\fs26 \cf4 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 This quiet oceanfront spot has it all\'97if you\'92re not surfing Shipwrecks right out the front of the house, check out the tide pools at low tide, find rocks and a decaying ship resting in the bay.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading20\partightenfactor0
\cf4 The neighborhood is safe, friendly, and laid-back. Beyond the gates, open land gives you a true sense of freedom, and the local town has supermarkets, restaurants and whatever you need.\
The Baja 1000 coastal route runs right outside the gates, perfect for watching off-roaders race up the coast.\

